PN,43703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1783675170
OL,3,CSupport and concern as councils
OL,4,Cconsider visitor levy
OL,6,FCardiff Council has already confirmed
OL,7,Fit will introduce the tax, while
OL,8,Fcouncils in Gwynedd, Conwy and
OL,9,FAnglesey have began consulting
OL,10,Fresidents and businesses before making
OL,11,Fa decision.
OL,13,FCommunities Under Pressure
OL,15,FNorthwest Wales attracts millions of
OL,16,Fvisitors every year, bringing
OL,17,Fsignificant economic benefits.
OL,19,FHowever, some residents say the
OL,20,Fpopularity of the region also brings
OL,21,Fchallenges.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
