SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1783675170
OL,3,CSupport and concern as councils
OL,4,Cconsider visitor levy
OL,6,FGwynedd Council says any money raised
OL,7,Fwould be reinvested into projects
OL,8,Fincluding beaches, parks, town
OL,9,Fcentres, cultural attractions,
OL,10,Fsustainable tourism initiatives and
OL,11,Fsupport for the Welsh language within
OL,12,Flocal communities.
OL,14,FAccording to Economist Dr Rhys ap
OL,15,FGwilym of Bangor University, tourism
OL,16,Fcontributes to around 10% of Gwynedd's
OL,17,Feconomy and supports approximately 15%
OL,18,Fof jobs in the county.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
